much for being with us today

00:58:38.520 --> 00:58:42.660
and I wanna show your
two books because I think

00:58:42.660 --> 00:58:46.430
they should be read because you are

00:58:46.430 --> 00:58:49.650
fearless in your willingness to discuss

00:58:50.930 --> 00:58:54.250
the issues that were raised by 9/11

00:58:54.250 --> 00:58:56.670
and the response of this administration.

00:58:56.670 --> 00:58:58.960
Thank you very much for
coming on our program.

00:58:58.960 --> 00:58:59.793
- Thank you, Harry.

00:58:59.793 --> 00:59:00.626
It's a pleasure.

